'''''Education in Chemistry''''' is a [[magazine]] covering all areas of [[chemistry education]],<ref name="ISTL" /> concentrating on the teaching of chemistry in [[secondary school]]s and [[university|universities]].<ref name="EiC-2014-09">{{cite journal |date=September 2014 |journal=Education in Chemistry |publisher=[[Royal Society of Chemistry]] |volume=51 |issue=5 |issn=0013-1350 |page=2 |title=Education in Chemistry}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Education in Chemistry relaunches with a new responsive site|date=24 January 2017|url=http://www.abacusemedia.com/education-in-chemistry-relaunches-with-a-new-responsive-site/449.blog|website=abacus e-media|accessdate=3 March 2017 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180726234444/https://www.abacusemedia.com/education-in-chemistry-relaunches-with-a-new-responsive-site/449.blog|archivedate=26 July 2018|deadurl=no}}</ref> The [[editor]] is Paul MacLellan.<ref>{{cite web|title=Contacts|url=https://eic.rsc.org/contacts|website=Education in Chemistry|publisher=Royal Society of Chemistry|accessdate=3 March 2017}}</ref> It is also available as an app for mobile devices.<ref name=DITlibrary-app>{{cite web|title=Education in Chemistry: new app and free issues for 2015|url=http://ditlibrary-scienceblog.blogspot.co.uk/2015/02/education-in-chemistry-new-app-and-free.html|website=DIT Library Kevin Street|accessdate=5 February 2015|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180629235805/https://ditlibrary-scienceblog.blogspot.com/2015/02/education-in-chemistry-new-app-and-free.html|archivedate=29 June 2018|deadurl=no}}</ref> It is published by the [[Royal Society of Chemistry]],<ref name="ABE-IPS">{{cite web |url=http://www.abe.pl/en/journal/1400/education-in-chemistry |title=Education in Chemistry - 0013-1350 |publisher=ABE-IPS |accessdate=22 September 2014|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180726234501/https://www.abe.pl/en/journal/1400/education-in-chemistry|archivedate=26 July 2018|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="RSC-EIC">{{cite web|url=https://eic.rsc.org|title=Education in Chemistry|publisher=[[Royal Society of Chemistry]]}}</ref> which also publishes ''[[Chemistry Education Research and Practice]]'', a [[peer-reviewed]] [[academic journal]] on the same topic.<ref name="ISTL">{{cite web|title=Selected Internet Resources on Chemistry Education|url=http://www.istl.org/14-fall/internet.html|website=Issues in Science & Technology Librarianship|publisher=Association of College & Research Libraries|accessdate=25 April 2016|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180726201827/http://www.istl.org/14-fall/internet.html|archivedate=26 July 2018|deadurl=no}}</ref>

